strings.Value: "I think I've lost an earring in all the tumult. Has anyone seen it?"
"Oh! I think I got my cheek scratched in that last fight! I hope it won't leave a scar!"
"You were barely standing for pain, and now your thoughts go to such petty things? You might be a trifle more serious!"
"She cannot go an hour without looking in a mirror. â€” A sure sign of feeble-mindedness!"
"Are you serious? Or just putting on a brave face, so we won't see you barely can stand?"
"Ha! You see that? My Octavia sure is tough!"
